[TITLE_SPANISH]Planos
[TITLE_ENGLISH]Planes

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]En esta lección vamos a añadir 2 planos de masa a la placa, uno en la capa <b>TOP</b> y otro en la <b>BOTTOM</b>
[ENGLISH]In this lesson we are going to add 2 ground planes to the PCB, one in the <b>TOP</b> layer and the other in the <b>BOTTOM</b> layer.
[SPANISH]Vamos a seleccionar la capa de cobre en TOP (<b>F.Cu</b>)
[ENGLISH]We are going to select the copper layer in TOP (<b>F.Cu</b>)
[END_LIST]
[IMG]01.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Vamos a usar la herramienta de añadir planos (<b>Add filled zones</b>)
[ENGLISH]We are going to use the add planes tool (<b>Add filled zones</b>)
[END_LIST]
[IMG]02.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Vamos a empezar por la esquina superior izquierda.
[ENGLISH]Let&#39s start at the upper left corner.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]03.png
[IMG]04.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Tenemos que especificar la capa (<b>F.Cu</b>) y la net (<b>GND</b>) del plano.
[ENGLISH]We have to specify the layer (<b>F.Cu</b>) and the net (<b>GND</b>) of the plane.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]05.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Traza el rectángulo del plano.
[ENGLISH]Draw the rectangle on the plane.
